English: <color=red>://ERROR: Door locked, unable to operate. Complete HSU scan to gain entrance.</color>
Description:
Don't localize HSU. 
A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

French.Translation: <color=red>://ERREUR : Porte verrouillée, ouverture impossible. Effectuez une analyse HSU pour entrer.</color>

Italian.Translation: <color=red>://ERRORE: porta bloccata e non funzionante. Completare scansione HSU per accedere.</color>

German.Translation: <color=red>://FEHLER: Tür verschlossen, keine Operation möglich. Führen Sie einen HSU-Scan durch, um Zugang zu erhalten.</color>

Spanish.Translation: <color=red>://ERROR: Puerta cerrada, no se puede operar. Completa el escaneo de las HSU para acceder.</color>

Russian.Translation: <color=red>://ОШИБКА. Дверь заблокирована. Для разблокировки завершите проверку HSU.</color>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: <color=red>://ERRO: Porta trancada, incapaz de operar. Conclua o escaneamento HSU para conseguir entrar.</color>

Polish.Translation: <color=red>://BŁĄD: drzwi zamknięte, sterowanie uniemożliwione. Aby uzyskać dostęp, ukończ skanowanie HSU.</color>

Japanese.Translation: <color=red>://エラー：ドアはロック中。作動不可。HSUスキャンを完了して進入。</color>

Korean.Translation: <color=red>://오류: 문이 폐쇄되어 작동할 수 없습니다. 진입하려면 HSU 스캔을 완료하십시오.</color>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: <color=red>://錯誤：門已上鎖，無法操作。完成HSU掃描以獲得進入權限。</color>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: <color=red>://错误：门已锁上，无法操作。完成HSU扫描以进入。</color>
